{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"15112b85-b9b8-40ca-b13c-ef628d2c075d","content":"No workflow files found in the current directory, so here's a general guide for the switch:\n\n### Changes needed for NuGet Trusted Publishing (OIDC)\n\n**1. On nuget.org** — register a Trusted Publisher:\n- Go to your package → **Manage** → **Trusted Publishers**\n- Add a GitHub Actions publisher: set your **repo**, **branch/tag pattern**, and optionally the **workflow filename** and **environment**\n\n**2. In your workflow** — three changes:\n\n```yaml\n# A) Add id-token permission at job level\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write   # ← required for OIDC\n      contents: read\n\n    # B) (Recommended) Use a GitHub environment matching what you registered\n    environment: nuget-publish\n\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      # ... build & pack steps ...\n\n      # C) Replace the dotnet nuget push that uses the API key:\n      #\n      # BEFORE:\n      #   dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }} --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n      #\n      # AFTER:\n      - uses: dotnet/nuget-push@v1       # official trusted-publish action\n        with:\n          source: https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n### Key differences\n\n| Before (API key) | After (OIDC) |\n|---|---|\n| `secrets.NUGET_API_KEY` | No secret needed |\n| `dotnet nuget push --api-key` | `dotnet/nuget-push@v1` action |\n| — | `permissions: id-token: write` |\n| — | Trusted Publisher registered on nuget.org |\n\nThe action exchanges the GitHub OIDC token for a short-lived NuGet publish token automatically—no long-lived secrets to rotate.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"64c1d692-eb54-471b-ad6f-fab968af414b","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"No workflow files found in the current directory. The user is asking a general question about switching from NuGet API key to OIDC trusted publishing. Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":534,"requestId":"0FC8:119996:16F3D65:1A1CF12:69E81A67"},"id":"2c82c329-5813-4d80-ab33-ba33778b82df","timestamp":"2026-04-22T00:46:43.872Z","parentId":"afd5799a-7a75-464a-a7e5-ba0787f78983"}
